  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用大量比喻或拟人的例子为您解释数据结构的定义</h2>无论您是正在学习数据结构专业课的学生，还是零基础想当解谜游戏顺便开拓思维。游玩完全无压力！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >活灵活现的演示动画</h2>动画是最直观的表现方式！多么精准简练的文字都不如动画更容易理解<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/e1b65557a53cf0d7fcc4fa02de58ff8d.poster.avif?t=1706146095\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/e1b65557a53cf0d7fcc4fa02de58ff8d.webm?t=1706146095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/e1b65557a53cf0d7fcc4fa02de58ff8d.mp4?t=1706146095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难度适中的互动解谜小游戏</h2>在掌握了概念之后，您总需要练练手！每当学习一个概念之后都会安排简单的小谜题<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/fa95a19bc2fef83268c4c762158178f9.poster.avif?t=1706146095\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/fa95a19bc2fef83268c4c762158178f9.webm?t=1706146095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/fa95a19bc2fef83268c4c762158178f9.mp4?t=1706146095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想自己试试看?</h2>在关卡中复制可以复刻本关过程与结果的代码.您可以随时导出到自己的编辑器中<br>自行编辑代码,结合游戏深度理解其中的原理与思想<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/e19c34cc45804835c937a33ee7c65687.poster.avif?t=1706146095\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/e19c34cc45804835c937a33ee7c65687.webm?t=1706146095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386840/extras/e19c34cc45804835c937a33ee7c65687.mp4?t=1706146095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
